# AfricaCryptoChainx (ACCX) Project Docs

This repository contains the official documentation for the AfricaCryptoChainx project. The project is currently in early development. If you encounter any issues or have suggestions, please open an issue.

**Owner & Sole Controller:** Patrickoto91 – `0x2f9e1ef59353ec41bf3e0aabbf734547c3d04444`

## Development

Install the [Mintlify CLI](https://www.npmjs.com/package/mint) to preview the documentation changes locally. To install, run:

```
npm i -g mint
```

Run the following command at the root of the repository (where `docs.json` is located):

```
mint dev
```

View the local preview at `http://localhost:3000`.

